tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE token_transfers (
    transfer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    sender_address VARCHAR(255),
    receiver_address VARCHAR(255),
    transfer_amount DECIMAL(18, 2),
    transfer_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE token_transfers (
  transfer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  token_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  sender_address VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  receiver_address VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  transfer_amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  transfer_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE token_owners (
  owner_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  token_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  owner_address VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  ownership_start_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  ownership_end_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE token_transfers (
    transfer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT NOT NULL,
    sender_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    recipient_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    transfer_amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    transfer_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE token_transfers (
    transfer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT NOT NULL,
    sender_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    receiver_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    transfer_amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    transaction_hash VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    transfer_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE tokens (
    token_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    token_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    token_symbol VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    total_supply DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    owner_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    sender_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    receiver_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    transfer_amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    transaction_hash VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    block_number INT NOT NULL,
    transaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE token_transfers (
    transfer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    from_address VARCHAR(255),
    to_address VARCHAR(255),
    amount DECIMAL,
    transfer_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE token_ownership (
    ownership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    owner_address VARCHAR(255),
    ownership_start TIMESTAMP,
    ownership_end TIMESTAMP
);
